  "texts": [
    "This selection provides a comprehensive comparison across different architectural paradigms.",
    "Generalization BenchmarksTo first establish the general feature extraction capability of our backbone, we benchmark it on the ImageNet-1K classification task [11].",
    "As shown in Table 1, PathMamba achieves a Top-1 accuracy of 83.1%, outperforming other leading architectures of a similar scale.",
    "This demonstrates the fundamental strength of our hybrid design.",
    "We further validate its versatility for dense prediction tasks on the challenging ADE20K dataset [51]."
  ]
